complexion having long hair reaching his earlobes which was the best hair of its sort and he had combed his hair and water was dropping from it and he was performing the tawaf around the kaba while he was leaning on two men or on the shoulders of two men i asked who is this man somebody replied he is messiah son of mary then i saw another man with very curly hair blind in the right eye which looked like a protruding out grape i asked who is this somebody replied he is messiah addajjal  sahih albukhari volume  book  number   joseph suad najmabadi afsaneh  encyclopedia of women  islamic cultures family body sexuality and health volume  boston brill academic publishers p  isbn    rashid ahmed  taliban islam oil and the new great game in central asia i b tauris  co ltd p  isbn    raghavan sudarsan  another freedom cut short iraqs barbers under threat the washington post archived from the original on    south asia  profile abdullah mehsud bbc news  retrieved    taliban leader hakimullah mehsud threatens us months after death the daily telegraph  retrieved    wong edward  iraqs sufis attacked as strife widens the new york times   kirk lowell  cherokee myths and legends retrieved    ferris jeri  native american doctor minneapolis carolrhoda books pp – isbn    kilcup karen  native american womens writing c – cambridge blackwell publishers pp – isbn    cavallo dominick  a fiction of the past new york st martins press p  isbn    nagel joane  american indian ethnic renewal oxford oxfordshire oxford university press p  isbn    french laurence  native american justice lanham rowman  littlefield publishers inc pp – isbn    fontana vincent  municipal liability aspen law  business publishers pp – isbn    hiernaux jean  the people of africa scribners p  isbn    byrd pp –  prasso sheridan  the asian mystique new york public affairs press pp – isbn    a b reid anthony  southeast asia in the age of commerce – new haven yale university press p  isbn    a b law kamyee  the chinese cultur