dly withers charm of ponniyin selvan the hindu retrieved  january    a b ponniyin selvan movie attempts – is it a curse or lack of purse  mgr – gemini ganeshan – vyjayanthimala bali com  may  retrieved  january    a b c randor guy  march  vanjikottai vaaliban  the hindu retrieved  january    subha j rao  february  memories of madras — shades of a bygone era the hindu retrieved  january    mega star mega film mega hype the hindu  june  retrieved  january    randor guy  september  beauty charm charisma the hindu retrieved  january    subhash k jha  december  ramanand sagar an obituary sify retrieved  january    a b randor guy  february  remembering pandari bai the indian express retrieved  november    k pradeep  november  dance and vyjayantimala the hindu retrieved  january    box office  box office india retrieved  january    randor guy  may  with a finger on peoples pulse the hindu retrieved  january    sra  october  stamp to honour sivaji the hindu chennai india retrieved  january    popular director yoganand passes away oneindiain  november  retrieved  february    director yoganand is no more indiaglitzcom  november  retrieved  february    randor guy  may  paarthibhan kanavu  the hindu retrieved  february    anjana rajan  january  screen stage and beyond the hindu coimbatore tamil nadu retrieved  february    box office  box office india retrieved  february    deepak mahan  march  gunga jamuna  the hindu retrieved  march    dinesh raheja  may  the tragic irony of ganga jumna rediff retrieved  march    gaurav malani  april  stardust classic ganga jumna  stardust retrieved  march    a b c box office  box office india retrieved  september    top earners  figures in ind rs box office india retrieved  march    a b nitin tej ahuja vajir singh saurabh sinha  november  top  film of last  years boxofficeindiacoin retrieved  march    the winners   the times of india retrieved  march    th annual bfja awards bfja archived from the original on  february  retrieved  march    sri  april  chit chat with jamuna telugucinemacom retrieved  march    tamil film director sridhar passes away the indian express  october  retrieved  october    v balasubramaniam  june  in a class of his own the hindu retrieved  march    cv sridhar veteran director passes away sify  october  retrieved  march    raja sen  february  jubilee hero rajendra kumar rediff retrieved  march    a p s malhotra  september  aas ka panchhi  the hindu retrieved  march    devinder bir kaur  july  melodrama was his forte the tribune retrieved  march    box office  box office india retrieved  march    down memory lane the indian express  november  retrieved  march    jasmine singh  november  hoton pe aisi baat the tribune chandigarh retrieved  november    surendra miglani  may  sangam revisited the tribune retrieved  march    suresh kohli  november  blast of the past  sangam  the hindu retrieved  march    raja sen  august  the  longest films in hindi cinema rediff retrieved  march    nonika singh  november  from naagin to nritya the tribune retrieved  march    ranjita biswas  october  bollywood embraces foreign backdrops asia times retrieved  march    rajiv vijayakar happily ever after deccan herald retrieved  march    dinesh raheja  may  the throbbing intensity of sangam rediff retrieved  march    a b c box office  box office india retrieved  march    a b top earners  figures in ind rs box office india retrieved  march    rana siddique zaman  august  china in bollywood the hindu retrieved  march    wani muthiah  february  dont underrate women in politics the hindu retrieved  march    dinesh raheja  may  tragedy king dilip kumar rediff retrieved  march    deepak mahaan  june  leader  the hindu retrieved  march    a b raju bharatan  july  dilip kumar and his women rediff retrieved  january    deepak mahaan  december  blast from the past zindagi  the hindu retrieved  march    ramanand sagar  man behind the ramayana outlook press trust of india  december  retrieved  march    mumbai mirror