t e filmfare award for lifetime achievement amitabh bachchan  dev anand  dilip kumar  lata mangeshkar  shammi kapoor  waheeda rehman  ashok kumar sunil dutt  vyjayanthimala  dharmendra mumtaz  pran  sharmila tagore  manoj kumar  helen  vinod khanna  hema malini  feroz khan  asha bhosle  gulzar  asha parekh  jeetendra  sulochana latkar nirupa roy  br chopra  rajesh khanna  shabana azmi  javed akhtar  jaya bachchan  rishi kapoor  bhanu athaiya  om puri  shashi kapoor  khayyam  manna dey  pyarelal  aruna irani  yash chopra  tanuja  kamini kaushal  moushumi chatterjee  authority control worldcat identities viaf  lccn n gnd  retrieved from httpsenwikipediaorgwindexphptitlevyjayanthimalaoldid categories thcentury indian actressesindian film actressesactresses in hindi cinema birthsliving peoplepoliticians from chennairecipients of the sangeet natak akademi awardindian actorpoliticiansth lok sabha membersth lok sabha membersperformers of indian classical dancebharatanatyam exponentsbharatiya janata party politiciansfemale carnatic singersbengal film journalists association award winnersindian national congress politicians from tamil naduindian women choreographersindian choreographersindian classical choreographersindian film choreographersindian female film singersbollywood playback singerswomen in tamil nadu politicstamil nadu politiciansindian dance teachersactresses in bengali cinemanominated members of the rajya sabhath lok sabha membersth lok sabha memberslok sabha members from tamil naduactresses from tamil nadurecipients of the padma shri in artsdancers from tamil naduthcentury indian dancerswomen artists from tamil naduindian women educatorsteachers of indian classical dancethcentury indian women artistseducators from tamil naduthcentury indian women politiciansthcentury indian educatorshidden categories cs tamillanguage sources taengvarb from september use dmy dates from september biography with signaturearticles with hcardswikipedia articles with viaf identifier