ided to step up in support of jaanleva  and will be leaving no stone unturned to promote the film prabhu deva and dancerturnedactress sudha chandran have also pledged their support for the film  asira tarannum tags sandeep malani janleva  dr vyjayanthimala bali big screen social cause bollywood facebook twitter pintrest google feedback next story arjun kapoor to work with father boney in a tamil remake related stories anant nag returns to bollywood after twodecade absence bollywood news  oct i am sridevis greatest fan ever bollywood news  oct kalpana pandit to make her bollywood debut bollywood news  sep more from jagran  comments leave a reply name  email  comment you have  characters left enter the text as shown in the image  send us feedback we value your feedback please provide us with your suggestions and comments send us your feedback help us understand what’s happeningabusive contentit’s a spam newsreport any site related issuethe user experience isn’t goodother feedback  suggestion trending mumbai how sena goon terrorised collapsed ghatkopar building residents national newsjul mumbai speeding car falls off bandra flyover  dead national newsjul gauri khan goes sunbathing with suhana and abram on beach bollywood newsjul revealed the real reason why mumait khan left bigg boss bollywood newsjul remember rinke khanna the actress who disappeared from bollywood bollywood newsjul photos twinkle khannas day out with bff anu dewan bollywood newsjul swiggy scam even we got a hard deal allege mumbai restaurateurs national newsjul mumbai crime molester dad asked daughters to massage his private parts national newsjul rosesh from sarabhai vs sarabhai takes on bharti singh television newsjul feast like a king at the new maharaja bhog outlet in lower parel food newsjul mumbai renowned ganpati idol maker vijay khatu passes away national newsjul trending most read most commented bcci wants indian cricket captain virat kohli to quit his job cricket newsjul bollywood actor inde