  boorback tapan sinha profile upperstallcom retrieved  july    a b c karan bali hatey bazarey upperstallcom retrieved  july    dinesh raheja  february  sadhanas song rediff retrieved  july    subhash k jha  january  will a hindumuslim love story work sify retrieved  july    anuj kumar  march  blast from the past sunghursh  the hindu retrieved  july    th annual bfja awards bfja archived from the original on  february  retrieved  july    vijay lokappally  november  saathi  the hindu retrieved  july    a b suresh kohli  february  duniya  the hindu retrieved  july    box office  box office india retrieved  july    karan bali mahesh kaul biography upperstall retrieved  may    nonika singh  november  from naagin to nritya the tribune retrieved  may    down memory lane the indian express  november  retrieved  may    jitendra kothari  october  nirupa roy eternal mother rediff retrieved  may    vyjayanthimala refuses rajinis maapilai in tamil oneindiain  april  retrieved  may    a b c d e t ramakrishnan rk radhakrishnan raktima bose  may  actor’s south chennai link the hindu retrieved  may    vandita mishra  august  gas leak outrage cutting through the fog the indian express retrieved  may    a b united news of india  august  vyjayanthimala quits congress the indian express retrieved  may    united news of india  august  vyjayanthimala quits congress the tribune new delhi retrieved  may    national events in  the hindu retrieved  may    independent india sify retrieved  may    coomi kapoor  october  personalised fiction anyone the star retrieved  january    bharati dubey  december  love in the time of flops the times of india retrieved  january    suresh kohli  january  celebrating the tragedy king the hindu retrieved  january    a b tavishi paitandy rastogi  september  vyjayanthimalas autobiography leaves kapoor clan fuming hindustan times new delhi india retrieved  january    bunny reuben  june  vignettes from the life of the showman the reign of raj rediff retrieved  january    united news of india  september  bunny reubens daughter speaks out in favour of rishi kapoor mumbai india oneindiain retrieved  january    on life and the arts the hindu chennai india  september    vyjayanthimala cineplotcom  may  retrieved  october   external linksedit wikimedia commons has media related to vyjayanthimala vyjayanthimala on imdb v t e filmfare award for best actress  meena kumari  meena kumari  kamini kaushal  nutan  nargis  vyjayanthimala  nutan   bina rai  vyjayanthimala  meena kumari  nutan  vyjayanthimala  meena kumari  waheeda rehman  nutan  waheeda rehman  sharmila tagore  mumtaz  asha parekh  hema malini  dimple kapadia  jaya bachchan  jaya bachchan  lakshmi  raakhee gulzar  shabana azmi  nutan  jaya bachchan   rekha  smita patil  padmini kolhapure  shabana azmi  shabana azmi  dimple kapadia  not awarded  not awarded  rekha  sridevi  madhuri dixit  sridevi  madhuri dixit  juhi chawla  madhuri dixit  kajol  karisma kapoor  madhuri dixit  kajol  aishwarya rai  present karisma kapoor  kajol  aishwarya rai  preity zinta  rani mukerji  rani mukerji  kajol  kareena kapoor  priyanka chopra  vidya balan  kajol  vidya balan  vidya balan  deepika padukone  kangana ranaut  deepika padukone  alia bhatt  v t e filmfare award for best supporting actress – usha kiran  nirupa roy  vyjayanthimala  shyama  nalini jaywant  lalita pawar  nanda  nirupa roy  shashikala  shashikala  nirupa roy  padmini  simi garewal  jamuna ramanarao  simi garewal  tanuja samarth  chaand usmani  farida jalal  zeenat aman  raakhee  durga khote  – nadira  kajri  asha sachdev  reena roy  helen  padmini kolhapure  supriya pathak  supriya pathak  rohini hattangadi  aruna irani  nutan  not awarded  not awarded  sonu walia  raakhee  rohini hattangadi  farida jalal  aruna irani  amrita singh  dimple kapadia  farida jalal  rekha  karisma kapoor  rani mukerji  sushmita sen  –present jaya bachchan  jaya bachchan  madhuri dixit  jaya bachchan  rani mukerji  ayesha kapur  konkona sen s